</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Audi 純電車 e-tron 50 SUV 現身，西九純電車展覽＋全線車系列陣</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/07/audi-e-tron-3/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=audi-e-tron-3</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 07 May 2022 07:53:01 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[audi]]></category><category><![CDATA[E-TRON]]></category><category><![CDATA[etron]]></category><category><![CDATA[EV]]></category><category><![CDATA[純電動車]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1098873</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Audi 最高配置的入門版豪華歐洲電動 SUV e-tron 近日正式登場，今次將會推出 2 款型號，分別為  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Audi <span lang="ZH-TW">最高配置的入門版豪華歐洲電動</span><span lang="EN-US"> SUV</span> e-tron 近日正式登場，今次將會推出 2 款型號，分別為 Audi e-tron 50 quattro 及 Audi e-tron 55 quattro premium。而 2022 年全新 Audi e-tron 車系車價由港幣 $699,800 起，最快可於今年 6 月交車，同場亦列出全線高性能汽車版本跑車及 SUV 車款。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120251-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098884" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120251-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120251-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120251-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120251-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120251-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120251-2048x1153.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120251-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>適逢新車抵港，Audi 於 5 月 7 至 8 日上午 11 時至晚上 7 時於西九文化區藝術公園的自由空間大盒內舉行「Audi I The Best of Both Worlds 純電與高性能展覽」，屆時將公開展出全新 Audi e-tron 50 quattro、全線 Audi e-tron 純電車系及一系列 Audi Sport RS 高性能車款。由於保障公共衛生安全，是次展覽入場名額有限，到場前需事先到訪 <a href="https://info.hk-audi.com/tc/article/136">https://info.hk-audi.com/tc/article/136</a> 預約，或致電 2291 0000 查詢。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120537-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098885" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120537-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120537-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120537-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120537-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120537-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120537-2048x1153.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120537-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120434-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1098886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120434-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120434-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120434-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120434-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120434-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120434-2048x1153.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120434-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220506_120422-scaled.jpg"><img 